description:
Sinbad was born and raised in Tison Village of the Parthevia Empire. When Sinbad was 14, he captured his first and the world`s first Dungeon, http://anidb.net/ch80566 [Baal], which was summoned by http://anidb.net/ch62750 [Yunan]. During his journeys, he recruited all of his future http://anidb.net/ch63616 [Kingdom]`s Generals.
Source: Magi Wiki, edited.
name: Sinbad
